45
00:03:50,190 --> 00:03:52,750
Those Feelings Within...

46
00:03:55,300 --> 00:03:59,260
I read that article about the
restoration work this morning, too.

47
00:03:59,430 --> 00:04:03,400
It's because so many of the buildings
in this city were brought from Manhome.

48
00:04:03,400 --> 00:04:07,740
Like the Teatro La Fenice and
the Accademia di Belle Arti, right?

49
00:04:07,740 --> 00:04:11,350
There's also the Basilica
di Santa Maria della Salute.

50
00:04:11,350 --> 00:04:14,820
There's another church too,
the Basilica di San Giorgio Maggiore.

51
00:04:14,820 --> 00:04:17,390
And the Chiesa del Redentore.

52
00:04:17,390 --> 00:04:23,420
Speaking of buildings brought over from Manhome,
Caffè Florian was brought over too, right?

53
00:04:23,420 --> 00:04:28,330
Yes. You can really get a sense of its
long history from the beautiful rooms inside.

54
00:04:28,330 --> 00:04:31,870
Oh, really? I wish I could see it.

55
00:04:31,870 --> 00:04:35,300
Wha-?! You've never been inside?

56
00:04:35,300 --> 00:04:36,300
