friends with the owner, Akari.

58
00:04:45,080 --> 00:04:48,520
Since we're on the subject,
why don't we go have some tea?

59
00:04:48,580 --> 00:04:51,890
Good idea. Let's go there for our break.

60
00:04:51,890 --> 00:04:54,790
Yay! I get to see the inside!

61
00:04:54,790 --> 00:04:57,130
I can't wait, President Aria!

62
00:04:57,130 --> 00:04:58,960
