68
00:05:32,130 --> 00:05:37,800
Students had to submit their designs, and then
the student who was chosen got to paint the wraps.

69
00:05:37,800 --> 00:05:40,430
I heard it was really competitive.

70
00:05:40,770 --> 00:05:45,970
