city's face while they do the restoration.

71
00:05:46,340 --> 00:05:51,040
Once the restoration work is complete,
there won't be a use for them anymore, right?

72
00:05:51,250 --> 00:05:57,590
But even if it's just for a short while,
they'll delight everyone, visitors and locals alike.

73
00:05:57,590 --> 00:06:03,350
So in a way, it's Neo-Venezia's very own
method of showing hospitality. How wonderful!

