Palazzo Grimani yesterday.

188
00:12:36,220 --> 00:12:38,490
He was just staring at the building.

189
00:12:38,490 --> 00:12:41,590
He was staring at Ca' d'Oro just now, as well.

190
00:12:41,590 --> 00:12:46,390
I wonder if he quit making sweets,
and is researching buildings now?

191
00:12:50,030 --> 00:12:52,090
Here you go, President Aria.

192
00:13:02,080 --> 00:13:05,770
