Sir, Ma'am, the bridge we're about to
pass under is the Ponte dell' Accademia.

194
00:13:26,100 --> 00:13:31,000
It's a reconstruction of a bridge that
used to be in Manhome's Venice.

195
00:13:31,170 --> 00:13:34,980
It looks like it's made of wood,
but the structure is actually made of steel.

196
00:13:34,980 --> 00:13:36,410
I see...

197
00:13:37,010 --> 00:13:39,250
It's headstrong, just like you.

198
00:13:39,250 --> 00:13:40,350
You think so?

199
00:13:40,350 --> 00:13:41,750
I sure do!

200
00:13:44,650 --> 00:13:49,390
