202
00:13:57,630 --> 00:13:58,830
Is something wrong?

203
00:13:59,970 --> 00:14:01,640
No, I'm sorry.

204
00:14:01,640 --> 00:14:06,200
Well then, ready? Say, "Campanile!"

205
00:14:11,250 --> 00:14:13,980
Thank you for all the wonderful memories today.

206
00:14:13,980 --> 00:14:16,180
The pleasure was ours.

207
00:14:16,180 --> 00:14:17,450
Thank you very much.

208
00:14:17,450 --> 00:14:19,250
I'd love to come again.

209
00:14:19,250 --> 00:14:21,660
When we do, please guide us again.

210
00:14:21,660 --> 00:14:23,690
We'll be looking forward to it.

211
00:14:23,690 --> 00:14:24,990
